text:
Handy checklist for COVID-19 vaccine eligibility:
1) Do I have lungs?
2) Do I interact with other humans?
3) Am I free of any legitimate medical contraindication for vaccination?

If you answered YES to all 3, then go get vaccinated!
#CovidVaccine #GetVaccinatedNow #COVID19
